#find() method

s=input("enter string")
print(s)
res=s.find("am")
print(res)

OUTPUT:

enter stringhow are you, i am fine
how are you, i am fine
15

#isupper() 

s=input("enter string")
print(s) 
res=s.isupper()
print(res)

OUTPUT
enter stringPYTHON
PYTHON
True

enter stringpython
python
False

#islower() 

s=input("enter string")
print(s) 
res=s.islower()
print(res)

OUTPUT:
enter stringpythoN
pythoN
False

enter stringpython programming
python programming
True


